OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChilly under cloudy skies with
OL,6,Frain through much of the morning,
OL,7,Ffalling as sleet or snow over the
OL,8,FPennines and Cheviot Hills. Rain
OL,9,Fgradually easing by the afternoon,
OL,10,Fthough remaining cloudy. Breezy
OL,11,Finitially, but winds soon falling
OL,12,Flight.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA cold night with variable
OL,15,Fcloud, clear spells and a widespread
OL,16,Ffrost. A few patches of mist and fog
OL,17,Fmay also develop in any prolonged
OL,18,Fclear skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,165,160,301,260,100,100
