OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start, any
OL,6,Fearly mist or fog patches will soon
OL,7,Fclear to give a drier, brighter day
OL,8,Fwith sunny spells, before turning
OL,9,Fcloudy again later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fcloudy with patchy drizzle Sunday.
OL,13,FAfter a murky start Monday, brighter
OL,14,Fspells likely to develop along with a
OL,15,Frisk of showers. Some brightness
OL,16,Finitially Tuesday but becoming
OL,17,Fincreasingly cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
